body:
For now, `Squeeze` is supported only when it can be fused into other ops. 

Please refer to [this doc](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/g3doc/tf_ops_compatibility.md) to see the ops compatibility. The team is working on supporting more ops in Toco and hopefully this will be supported in the near future.
